4719struct ucd_decomposition_info {
4720 constexpr static unsigned cp_index_width = 15;
4721 constexpr static unsigned cp_size_width = 5;
4722 constexpr static unsigned type_width = 5;
4723
4724 using value_type = uint32_t;
4725 static_assert(cp_index_width + cp_size_width + type_width <= sizeof(value_type) * CHAR_BIT);
4726
4727 value_type value;
4728
4731 [[nodiscard]] constexpr size_t cp_index() const noexcept
4732 {
4733 return value >> (cp_size_width + type_width);
4734 }
4735
4738 [[nodiscard]] constexpr size_t cp_size() const noexcept
4739 {
4740 constexpr auto mask = (value_type{1} << cp_size_width) - 1;
4741 return (value >> type_width) & mask;
4742 }
4743
4746 [[nodiscard]] constexpr unicode_decomposition_type type() const noexcept
4747 {
4748 constexpr auto mask = (value_type{1} << type_width) - 1;
4749 return static_cast<unicode_decomposition_type>(value & mask);
4750 }
4751
4757 [[nodiscard]] constexpr bool should_decompose(size_t decomposition_mask) const noexcept
4758 {
4759 return to_bool((1_uz << std::to_underlying(type())) & decomposition_mask) and cp_size() != 0;
4760 }
4761
4768 [[nodiscard]] constexpr std::u32string decompose() const noexcept
4769 {
4770 auto r = std::u32string{};
4771 hilet first = cp_index() * detail::ucd_decompositions_code_point_width;
4772 hilet last = first + cp_size() * detail::ucd_decompositions_code_point_width;
4773
4774 for (auto i = first; i != last; i += detail::ucd_decompositions_code_point_width) {
4775 r += wide_cast<char32_t>(load_bits_be<detail::ucd_decompositions_code_point_width>(
4776 detail::ucd_decomposition_code_points_bytes, i));
4777 }
4778 return r;
4779 }
4780
4787 [[nodiscard]] constexpr std::optional<char32_t> canonical_equivalent() const noexcept
4788 {
4789 if (type() == unicode_decomposition_type::canonical and cp_size() == 1) {
4790 hilet offset = cp_index() * detail::ucd_decompositions_code_point_width;
4791 return char_cast<char32_t>(load_bits_be<detail::ucd_decompositions_code_point_width>(detail::ucd_decomposition_code_points_bytes, offset));
4792 } else {
4793 return std::nullopt;
4794 }
4795 }
4796};

4800[[nodiscard]] constexpr ucd_decomposition_info ucd_get_decomposition(char32_t code_point) noexcept
4801{
4802 constexpr auto max_code_point_hi = detail::ucd_decompositions_indices_size - 1;
4803
4804 auto code_point_hi = code_point / detail::ucd_decompositions_chunk_size;
4805 hilet code_point_lo = code_point % detail::ucd_decompositions_chunk_size;
4806
4807 if (code_point_hi > max_code_point_hi) {
4808 code_point_hi = max_code_point_hi;
4809 }
4810
4811 // The index in the chunk-index table based on the upper-bits of the code-point.
4812 hilet chunk_index = load_bits_be<detail::ucd_decompositions_index_width>(
4813 detail::ucd_decompositions_indices_bytes,
4814 code_point_hi * detail::ucd_decompositions_index_width);
4815
4816 // Add back in the lower-bits of the code-point.
4817 hilet index = (chunk_index * detail::ucd_decompositions_chunk_size) + code_point_lo;
4818
4819 // Get the decomposition value from the decomposition table by index.
4820 hilet value = load_bits_be<detail::ucd_decomposition_width>(
4821 detail::ucd_decompositions_bytes, index * detail::ucd_decomposition_width);
4822
4823 return ucd_decomposition_info{narrow_cast<ucd_decomposition_info::value_type>(value)};
4824}
